{"tid":1419110,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我地唔控制我地怒火 就會輸","createTime":"2019-08-05T23:49:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T00:25:58.000Z","uid":181945,"like":29,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"483d1b78e24982b39fe337eca45ea83833b44818","tid":1419110,"uid":181945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:49:55.000Z","msg":"利申我未係最前線一批 發夢主要中後支援物資站<br />\n <br />\n黑警濫權、政治拘捕、插贓嫁禍、除褲遊街、人肉錄音，我都嬲，我都好嬲。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係大佬，越嬲，我地就越要用腦做嘢！</span><br />\n<br />\n一開始，我地嘅遊行質素名威國際，外媒爭住報道，贏得唔少掌聲，而手足士氣都好高昂。<br />\n<br />\n宜家？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n由㩒住手足唔破壞，到<span style=\"color: red;\">周街見到交通燈塗鴉</span>。<br />\n由和理勇只起路障保護自己，到<span style=\"color: red;\">無人撩都主動掉嘢入警局</span>。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n我知大家每個星期，一至五返工，六日出黎馬拉松，會攰，會嬲，會無力。<br />\n<br />\n如果嬲就出言侮罵，就到處破壞，我地同班警察<span style=\"color: red;\">有咩分別？</span><br />\n<br />\n你可能話，成個運動咁多人，我都做唔到啲咩架啦。咁咪由自己開始囉。<br />\n<br />\n警察換裝縱火，就係想民意倒戈。做好自己，拉埋幾個手液阻止佢。<br />\n見人噴漆噴文物建築。做好自己，勸佢去第二度。<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。係啊，好浪漫啊。浪漫背後要用腦分拆利弊，諗策略，唔係一味衝發洩。<br />\n<br />\n一句講哂。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">控制你對手，真正顯出你係有腦嘅真。香港人。</span></span>"},{"pid":"1d8ca0d5bcfaa18e9d454cb5b1a60ebc89e927e2","tid":1419110,"uid":258342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:50:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"78bd572261fdceeafa987a952cd76fa1a36aa68d","tid":1419110,"uid":111796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:52:53.000Z","msg":"Push, 唔好俾怒火同理智充昏頭腦"},{"pid":"2f439ba708fd6e0b0a39f0f447627e23d756139a","tid":1419110,"uid":143151,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:53:33.000Z","msg":"咁我哋可以做啲咩？<br />\n政府一冷處理 就玩完"},{"pid":"b7004ded77b7310f0a923a3ed9968035187dc639","tid":1419110,"uid":134227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d723178588de1d42e67f0bb7f3b97035cf6f22","tid":1419110,"uid":269655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:55:14.000Z","msg":"唔好俾仇恨支配 冷靜一點"},{"pid":"c48eec7a31b40621af39316528326c4a2009f905","tid":1419110,"uid":181945,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2f439ba708fd6e0b0a39f0f447627e23d756139a","tid":1419110,"uid":143151,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:53:33.000Z","msg":"咁我哋可以做啲咩？<br />\n政府一冷處理 就玩完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:07:06.000Z","msg":"唔亂咁發洩 都可以用其他方法<br />\n如果有號召力 可以領口號/mo人去邊度邊度企/行<br />\n<br />\n尤其我哋前嗰幾日有咁多次成功嘅Be Water經驗"},{"pid":"1d8f78561eb2aff9c97f3a333844c0a95f200126","tid":1419110,"uid":29093,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:08:23.000Z","msg":"依啲 有智慧既 post 就無人推"},{"pid":"ec2afe46df25d58b0efcd73c0d883ad89300dd32","tid":1419110,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:09:17.000Z","msg":"成晚就推埋哂啲  鼓吹武力無限升級既話題 <br />\n<br />\n武力無限升級根本唔會幫到件事"},{"pid":"e2074d962d773a7b525df70b1b2672c1d917c6c3","tid":1419110,"uid":211524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:11:58.000Z","msg":"大家其實要冷靜<br />\n唔好比仇恨蒙蔽雙眼 ！"},{"pid":"fa97dad8242e469ad56a3ea223e2a31b384b0cc2","tid":1419110,"uid":181945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d8f78561eb2aff9c97f3a333844c0a95f200126","tid":1419110,"uid":29093,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:08:23.000Z","msg":"依啲 有智慧既 post 就無人推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:15:19.000Z","msg":"大家太嬲喇 盡力就得"},{"pid":"bf0e18c575fecfd99cfe9ea03e767a1fe997abb4","tid":1419110,"uid":199050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:25:58.000Z","msg":"班勇武未起身，推撚到佢地睇到為止"}]}